text: Zett Jukassa was a young Jedi who lived on the planet Coruscant with the rest of the Jedi Order. Zett is in Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones. He is killed in Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith. He was fighting bravelyagainst Clone troopers. ==Behind the scenes== Zett Jukassa is played by Star Wars creator George Lucas's son, Jett Lucas. ==References== Category:Star Wars characters
